# IntelliJ HTTP Client examples for technical-interview-demo
# These paths are intended for trusted internal or devops validation, not for the
# supported external `/api/**` contract.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### TechnicalOverviewController - internal root technical overview
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json

### TechnicalOverviewController - internal hello smoke endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/hello
Accept: text/plain
